---- USER STORY #8----

#8 As a user, I can view other users' saved shapes if they choose to share (upload) them.

  a) Description:

      A user can see both their own shapes and others shapes, but only if others share them.

      Users cannot view shapes that are not shared and approved by an administrator.

      

  b) Tasks:
  
       As a user, I can view other users' saved shapes that are shared.

       As an administrator, I can approve which shapes a user can view by approving or rejecting pending shapes that are requesting to be shared.


  c) Tests:
       Verify that a user can view their own shapes online.
       Verify that a user can view other users' approved shapes.
       Verify that users cannot view unshared shapes.
       Verify that administrators can approve and reject pending shapes.
       Verify that users cannot view rejected shapes.
  d) Assignee:
       ???
  e) Estimation: ??
  f) Priority: ??
  g) Done:
       A user is able to view their own shapes.
       Administrators are able to approve and reject pending shapes.
       A user cannot view unshared or rejected shapes.
